est and set `spring.cloud.stream.kafka.binder.brokers` to its bootstrap address before refreshing the binder/application context. Exercise a real producer and consumer binding against a unique topic; do not allow the binder to use its default `localhost:9092`.\",\"risks\":[\"No Kafka Docker image is currently pinned in the repository allow-list, so an embedded broker is the deterministic option. Native Image verification may expose embedded-broker reachability limitations; Gradle and Native Image results remain authoritative.\"]}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00dfa1818285bdc1016a4ecc768aa48191919cf00dc5e21628\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-codex-responses", "provider": "openai-codex", "model": "gpt-5.6-terra", "usage": {"input": 1229, "output": 738, "cacheRead": 44544, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 46511, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1783549035043, "responseId": "resp_00dfa1818285bdc1016a4ecc6b7520819194eca208581c29f2"}, "toolResults": []}
